CRITICAL Vue + Vite WebContainer Rules:
- package.json MUST have "type": "module"
- vite.config.ts uses ESM imports
- index.html MUST exist at project root with <script type="module" src="/src/main.ts">
- ALWAYS use `npm run dev` to start â€” never use bare `vite`
- Vue single-file components (.vue) use <script setup lang="ts"> for TypeScript
